Page viewed:
SELECT
    uuid as event_id,
    person.id as person_id,
    person.properties.$os as person_os,
    person.properties.$browser as person_browser,
    person.properties.$device_type as person_device,
    person.properties.$geoip_city_name as person_city,
    person.properties.$geoip_postal_code as person_postal_code,
    person.properties.$geoip_country_name as person_country,
    timestamp as time,
    coalesce(properties.$current_url, properties.$screen_name) as url
FROM events
WHERE event = 'Page viewed'
and timestamp > toTimeZone(toDateTime('2024-04-24 00:00:00'),'Europe/Paris')
and not (properties.$current_url LIKE '%localhost%' or properties.$current_url LIKE '%127.0.0.1%')
ORDER BY timestamp DESC  LIMIT 10000000
Platform button clicked:
SELECT
    uuid as event_id,
    person.id as person_id,
    person.properties.$os as person_os,
    person.properties.$browser as person_browser,
    person.properties.$device_type as person_device,
    person.properties.$geoip_city_name as person_city,
    person.properties.$geoip_postal_code as person_postal_code,
    person.properties.$geoip_country_name as person_country,
    timestamp as time,
    properties.$platform as platform
FROM events
WHERE event = 'Platform button clicked'
and timestamp > toTimeZone(toDateTime('2024-04-24 00:00:00'),'Europe/Paris')
and not (properties.$current_url LIKE '%localhost%' or properties.$current_url LIKE '%127.0.0.1%')
ORDER BY timestamp DESC  LIMIT 10000000
